            "query": "fetch spans\n| filter isNotNull(gen_ai.provider.name) AND in(llm.request.type, {\"chat\", \"completion\"})\n| fieldsAdd inputTokens = toDouble(gen_ai.usage.input_tokens)\n| fieldsAdd outputTokens = toDouble(gen_ai.usage.output_tokens)\n| summarize totalTokens = sum(inputTokens) + sum(outputTokens)",
